Fuck you.

97
00:05:42,135 --> 00:05:44,479
(VOICES OVERLAPPING)

98
00:05:44,480 --> 00:05:47,817
(JERRY CONTINUES) Two days later at
our corporate conference in Miami,

99
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:51,154
A breakthrough.
