Boy, guys, it's a real
bruiser out there tonight.

1931
01:57:14,504 --> 01:57:19,039
MICHAELS: the cardinals just refuse
to go quietly into the desert night,

1932
01:57:19,040 --> 01:57:21,542
As their seemingly interminable
season winds down.

1933
