No, wait, wait. Just let me
enjoy this for a minute.

2018
02:01:56,170 --> 02:01:59,402
DIERDORF: You're looking for
any movement out of Rod Tidwell.

2019
02:01:59,403 --> 02:02:01,748
Is that his head
coming up I see?

2020
02:02:01,749 --> 02:02:04,616
GIFFORD: He's going
to try to get up.

2021
