I love you, Tyson!

2070
02:05:32,972 --> 02:05:36,830
I love you, baby! How's the baby?
How's Kaydee?

2071
02:05:36,831 --> 02:05:39,959
(SOBBING, LAUGHING)
oh, I love you so much.

2072
02:05:39,960 --> 02:05:41,939
(LAUGHS)

