2084
02:06:30,954 --> 02:06:34,707
(CHATTERING CONTINUES)

2085
02:06:34,916 --> 02:06:37,940
(WOMAN LAUGHING)

2086
02:06:37,941 --> 02:06:41,069
You know what?
I have a confession to make.

2087
